item.title: Aarushi Paingankar
item.description: Instructions Delete all of this and paste in your own content right here!! Portfolio File Format To create a new Portfolio entry, make sure that you selected R Markdown (.Rmd) as the format option of the post when using the New Post blogdown addin. Setup chunk Make sure you edit the setup chunk above and bring in all packages you need using r library(package_name). Inserting a Custom image in your Post The easiest option is to use the blogdown Insert Image RStudio addin to add an external image.
